            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>數據狗(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DDOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DDOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DDOG-US</a>)截至台北時間21日22:38股價上漲5.86美元，報122.86美元，漲幅5.01%，成交量546,521（股），盤中最高價122.86美元、最低價118.75美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.45%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.35%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.19%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.21%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>數據狗(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DDOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DDOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DDOG-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-5.16%</li> <li>近 1 月：-15.22%</li> <li>近 3 月：-23.85%</li> <li>近 6 月：-18.07%</li> <li>今年以來：-11.03%</li></ul></section></main>",
